lyrics:
[Verse]
Tetra Pak, shining bright, a brand we hold dear
Delivering food safety and best quality, year after year
Leading the sustainability transformation, oh so clear
Integrating and optimizing, customer operation without fear

[Chorus]
Innovating for customer growth, a step beyond the norm
Tetra Pak, our beacon, keeping us warm
With strengthened leadership behaviors, we'll never conform
Together we'll thrive, in this harmonious swarm
